### 健康检查
GET http://localhost:8000/api/health

---

### 流式对话
POST http://localhost:8000/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "session_id": "test-session-001",
  "message": "你好，介绍一下你自己",
  "stream_mode": "messages"
}


### 非流式对话
POST http://localhost:8000/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "session_id": "test-session-001",
  "message": "你好",
  "stream_mode": "default"
}


### Human-in-the-loop 命令接口（Phase 1 暂未实现）
POST http://localhost:8000/api/chat/command
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "session_id": "test-session-001",
  "command": {
    "action": "continue"
  }
}
